      "text": "They’re $120 per kilo."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How many apples do you need?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "About four apples."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That’s roughly one kilo."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great, I’ll take one kilo."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want them in a bag?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, please."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Would you like to pick them yourself?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I’ll pick them."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look for firm ones without bruises."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you need anything else weighed?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, half a kilo of tomatoes."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sure. Do you want cherry tomatoes or regular?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Regular tomatoes."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I’ll weigh them for you."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is 0.52 kilo. Is that okay?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, that’s fine."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want them a bit riper or less ripe?"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Less ripe, please."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay. I’ll switch a couple."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All set. Here’s your label."
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great."
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Enjoy!"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks!"
    }
